## Multi-node clusters

You can also have a cluster with multiple control-plane & worker nodes, create a config file.

```

kind: Cluster
apiVersion: kind.x-k8s.io/v1alpha4
nodes:
- role: control-plane
  image: kindest/node:v1.32.1
- role: worker
  image: kindest/node:v1.32.1
- role: worker
  image: kindest/node:v1.32.1
- role: worker
  image: kindest/node:v1.32.1
  extraPortMappings:
  - containerPort: 80
    hostPort: 80
    protocol: tcp

```



